{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                 // hydrogen // schema // reactive // viewport"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Viewport — A first-class container for displaying content."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | A Viewport is NOT just \"the browser window.\" It's a **bounded viewing region**"},{"LineComment":" | with its own identity, settings, and controls. Think:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - A video player viewport (with playback controls, fullscreen toggle)"},{"LineComment":" | - A document viewport (with zoom, scroll position, page navigation)"},{"LineComment":" | - A 3D scene viewport (with camera controls, render settings)"},{"LineComment":" | - A dashboard viewport (with widget arrangement, refresh interval)"},{"LineComment":" | - A code editor viewport (with syntax highlighting, line numbers)"},{"LineComment":" | - A split pane viewport (one of N viewports in a layout)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Each viewport has:"},{"LineComment":" | - **Identity** (UUID5) — deterministic, reproducible across sessions"},{"LineComment":" | - **Dimensions** — current width/height in CSS pixels"},{"LineComment":" | - **Settings** — configuration specific to the content type"},{"LineComment":" | - **Controls** — actions available to manipulate the viewport"},{"LineComment":" | - **Content** — what's being displayed (polymorphic)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Breakpoints vs Viewport"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Breakpoints describe **size thresholds** — they're properties OF a viewport."},{"LineComment":" | A viewport IS the container; breakpoints describe its current state."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Container Queries"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Modern responsive design responds to **container size**, not just window size."},{"LineComment":" | A Viewport naturally supports this — its dimensions are always known,"},{"LineComment":" | independent of the browser window."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This is a leader module that re-exports from submodules:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - `Viewport.Types` — Core type definitions"},{"LineComment":" | - `Viewport.Breakpoints` — Breakpoint values and detection"},{"LineComment":" | - `Viewport.Core` — Viewport type, constructors, accessors"},{"LineComment":" | - `Viewport.Responsive` — Responsive value system"},{"LineComment":" | - `Viewport.CSS` — CSS generation utilities"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Usage"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Reactive.Viewport as Viewport"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Create a viewport for a dashboard"},{"LineComment":" | dashboardViewport = Viewport.viewport"},{"LineComment":" |   { namespace: \"acme-corp\""},{"LineComment":" |   , name: \"main-dashboard\""},{"LineComment":" |   , width: 1920"},{"LineComment":" |   , height: 1080"},{"LineComment":" |   }"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Get deterministic ID"},{"LineComment":" | Viewport.getId dashboardViewport  -- ViewportId \"a3f8c2d1-...\""},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Query current breakpoint"},{"LineComment":" | Viewport.getBreakpoint dashboardViewport  -- Xxl"},{"LineComment":" | ```"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[76,68],"start":[76,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","Viewport","Breakpoints"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[79,52],"start":[79,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Reactive","Viewport","CSS"]},{"annotation":{"meta":n